### [브랜드] Campaign 진행 관련
### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 1) 브랜드 입장에서 특정 캠페인에 대한 크리에이터 신청 현황 조회 (브랜드)
###    (캠페인 신청 목록 조회)
### GET /api//v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/acceptances/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/13/acceptances/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 2) 브랜드가 크리에이터 승인
### PATCH /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/acceptances/{acceptance_id}/approve/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/13/acceptances/13/approve/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 3) 브랜드가 크리에이터 거절
### PATCH /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/acceptances/{acceptance_id}/reject/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/13/acceptances/14/reject/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json



### ------------------------------------------------------------
### 6) 캠페인 진행 상황(Deliverables) 조회
### GET /api/v1/brand/{brand_id}/campaign/{campaign_id}/progress/
### ------------------------------------------------------------
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/brand/2/campaign/3/progress/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
